description:
Part 2 of 4 - "Agents of Satan" is a tactful, passionate, biblical response to false teaching - especially on the Internet - against the Ten Commandments and Commandment-keepers. Co-hosted by Steve Wohlberg and Pastor Mark Howard, this unique 4-part TV series is based on one primary apocalyptic prediction: "The dragon was enraged with the woman and went to make war with the remnant of her seed, which keep the commandments of God and have the testimony of Jesus Christ"  (Revelation 12:17). Unfortunately, Satan's warfare is conducted through "agents" who, in the words of Jesus Christ, "know not what they do" (Luke 23:34). "Agents of Satan" is perfect for sharing with anyone confused about the Ten Commandments, "written with the finger of God" (Exodus 31:18), and their proper relationship to the gospel of Jesus Christ (see 1 Corinthians 15:1-4).
